{"type": "article", "id": 29286, "title": "混凝土制冷容器", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-07T23:03:28Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607071906201YkuEln9mXLSbBcQ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>还在用装满冰块的桶为酒制冷吗？Francisco Corvi 为芝加哥品牌 <a href=\"http://intoconcrete.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">IntoConcrete</a> 设计了一款混凝土材质的制冷容器，不仅实用，造型也很别致。说到混凝土，我们会把它和笨重联系在一起，采用先进铸造技术手工制作而成的 Corvi Cooler 仅重 1.8 千克，外形简洁而且还能侧放堆叠在一起。只需要把它们放在冰箱里冰上一段时间，Corvi Cooler 就能为美酒提供长时间的制冷效果。这是它的<a href=\"http://intoconcrete.com/products/corvi-wine-cooler-and-rack\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 85 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707190642uc3z1kVsQmnUSD0B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070719064260tP1qm9vNfAOXRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707190642vCfLPcBnyYmzVAkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160707190643qzGgLtFrJuXUn12f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}